Court sentenced defendant to serve 4 DAYS in the House of Correction CONSECUTIVE to any sentence with credit for 4 days; TIME SERVED. 
- Court sets Restitution at $0 (zero)
- No fine
- No driver license suspension
- Pay the mandatory DNA surcharge
- Pay all costs, fees, assessments and surcharges.  DNA surcharge and other costs, fees, assessments and surcharges are to be paid by 02-06-2017.  Failure to pay will result in a civil judgment.

Appeal rights given.  Notice of Right to Seek Postconviction Relief received and filed.

Defendant was advised of constitutional rights and maximum penalties, waived all rights, and plead GUILTY to the amended charge.  Defendant examined as to the plea. Court found the Defendant guilty of the amended charge and enters judgment of conviction into the record forthwith. 

Parties are prepared to proceed to sentencing.
